      "id": "PopularPost154869",
      "post_content": "I use this card in my [Grand Architect](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Grand Architect) deck. Excellent one drop that blocks the two first turns then taps for 2 mana on my third, letting me drop a [wurmcoil engine](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=wurmcoil engine) or a [steel hellkite](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=steel hellkite) :)  \n  \nT1: Kraken Hatchling  \nT2: [Etherium Sculptor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Etherium Sculptor)  \nT3: [Grand Architect](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Grand Architect), tap all 3 blues and get 6 mana (+1 mana cost reduction from the sculptor), drop any artifact that costs 7 CMC or less.",
      "posted_by": "Sleazebag",
