    {
      "id": "PopularPost26344",
      "post_content": "I like it - great for blue control, as has been said. Locks down the ground early against aggro, which keeps those [Vampire Lacerator](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Vampire Lacerator)s and [Scythe Tiger](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Scythe Tiger)s from getting through early, which can mean a dangerous drop in tempo/life for the opponent.  \n  \nAnd I agree with Bent - not every card should have an awesome or interesting ability, that's just poor card design. The combination of power, toughness, and cost here offers enough interesting gameplay possibilities as it is.",
      "posted_by": "RobinHood3000",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost26344\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">I like it - great for blue control, as has been said.  Locks down the ground early against aggro, which keeps those <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Vampire Lacerator\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Vampire Lacerator\">Vampire Lacerator</a>s and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Scythe Tiger\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Scythe Tiger\">Scythe Tiger</a>s from getting through early, which can mean a dangerous drop in tempo/life for the opponent.<br/><br/>And I agree with Bent - not every card should have an awesome or interesting ability, that's just poor card design.  The combination of power, toughness, and cost here offers enough interesting gameplay possibilities as it is.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '26344'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy709\">RobinHood3000</span>\r\n                                (9/29/2009 6:43:45 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl